This code get records by checking the location around 50 miles, but how i can check if there is no record around 50 mi. I want to show a message to user that no records find .

    {% set params = "orderBy=geo_distance(location,"  request.query_dict['lat']  ","  request.query_dict['lng']  ")" %}
          {% set params = "geo_distance(coordinate,"  request.query_dict['lat']  ","  request.query_dict['lng']  ",mi)__lt=50.0&amp;" ~ params %}

           {% for row in hubdb_table_rows(table_id, params) %}

